race.description: Aviso Tas Insurance Brokers Maiden Plate
race.comment: MAGNOLIA SKY (13) made debut this course and distance when double figure odds but ran well. Sat second throughout and boxed on well to finish fourth but will be much improved and drawn for a good trial. Can feature. GEEGEES MERCEDES (11) has placed two of four this time in and is close to getting off the mark. Beaten only a couple of lengths in a good form race last time when gave a sight and despite a tricky gate should be be ninths for a long way. LAWRENNY BOYS (4) was moderate fresh then improved sharply last time to finish runner-up in the same race as GEEGEES MERCEDES. Also has a wide gate to overcome but looks ready to win. CARDIOSPHERE (1) crossed fro wide out last time and gave a sight but was swamped late. Better draw here and with good speed will be in this for a long way.  ALFARINO (3) was well in the market on debut but raced below expectations. Blinkers added and can improve sharply.
